      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOTT SIGMA (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.00) in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Has a good record here including two wins. Has performed well from this box with a win and seven minor placings to her name from 10 starts. Rates on top in this line up. NANCY DEVERE (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 34.61 beating Reaper. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. Should feature again. UNCLE STILTSKIN (8) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that clocked a solid 29.95 win over 520m at Geelong. Expected to feature on best figures. TRIBECA (4) missed the frame latest (22.73) when seventh over 390m at Ballarat in a Grade 4/5. Has three wins already from this draw.",
